  "abstract": "In accordance with the Privacy Act, the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (Board) is amending its Rules Regarding Access to Personal Information under the Privacy Act to include a new system of records, entitled Multi-rater Feedback Records (BGFRS-25) to the list of system of records that is exempt from certain required disclosures. Notice of the new system of records is published elsewhere in this Federal Register.",
